quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  83,7,"Nay! Truly, the Record (writing of the deeds) of the Fujjâr (disbelievers, polytheists, sinners, evil-doers and the wicked) is (preserved) in Sijjîn."
  83,8,"And what will make you know what Sijjîn is?"
  83,9,"A Register inscribed."
  83,10,"Woe, that Day, to those who deny."